snippet.title: Dungeon Rats Trailer
snippet.description:
A turn-based, party-based dungeon crawler set in the Age of Decadence world.

Dungeon Rats will be released on Steam, GOG, and GamersGate on November 4th, 2016

http://store.steampowered.com/app/531930/

Learn more about the game on our website: 

http://www.irontowerstudio.com/

http://irontowerstudio.com/dungeon-rats-features

Or follow us in Facebook and Twitter:

http://www.facebook.com/IronTowerStudio

http://twitter.com/IronTowerStudio
